    <item>
      <title>英国工党改变免税养老金限额计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/uk-s-labour-party-u-turns-on-plans-for-tax-free-pension-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国五大政党本周准备发布各自的竞选宣言，而各方对于如何兑现竞选承诺存在疑问，而英国反对党工党已放弃重新引入养老金储蓄免税限额的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/uk-s-labour-party-u-turns-on-plans-for-tax-free-pension-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 22:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
